summary: It was in my sleepless night, moments where I contemplate - I realized in between my palpitations and worries that, what if,...
body:
It was in my sleepless night, moments where I contemplate - I realized in between my palpitations and worries that, what if, what if I lost you for good?

And it came to the conclusion that, I would love to lift your veil and kiss you, and know that I will never lose you.

@novembrely
